reviewText: I bought this as a gift for my mother as she enjoys listening to the group and Amazon.com was the only place I was able to find and purchase at a good price. My mother enjoys watching this DVD.
all i can say about canton junction......what a blessing.....the songs make u smile...laugh and feel gods presences...these men are very blessed

This is one fantastic DVD and should not be missed!  All four singers are extremely passionate about the message they give.  They are obviously bonded in an unusual way, and are also a lot of fun to watch.  I always say that one has to SEE Aaron Crabb sing to fully appreciate him, and this DVD proves that.  And I--and the audience--very much like Tim Duncan's spectacular bass voice.  The songs selected cover a wide range of Gospel music, and the bonus numbers are fabulous!  A DVD that carries a lot of joy and inspiration!
This is a great DVD with alot of wonderful songs on it.  I have listened to it several times.
Lovee it
Watch this DVD every week... so inspiring, and uplifting!  I love it!
Amazing group, I watched this probably 4 or 5 times already, love Tim Duncan as the bass singer.
Content is outstanding.  I love it.
Canton Junction arrived on time in excellent condition.  It is a great DVD.  I especially enjoyed Tim Duncan's great base voice.  Thanks.
We were looking for the bass singer and found him here...
I love this quartet and this DVD is just what I thought it would be.  Fantastic !!!  Love the songs on it
Love the anointing and feeling of being right there in the church. Great production and quality product. Great to actually "see" and hear the performance.
I bought this for my wife, which likes Canton Junction. So this  was a great idea she loves it thanks

CD arrived but would not play. My machine said it was a 'BAD DISC'. So, I returned it February 24, 2014, but so far have not heard from where I ordered it( it is now March 17, 2014). Hope to do so soon.
These guys are the best southern gospel singers I've heard. My husband and I enjoyed watching the DVD and hereing the best music.
love it want more listen to it all the time.will be bying it in thr future on cd as well

BEST DVD EVER!!  I watch this almost every night.  I sing, cry, praise, dance and excercise while i watch it. That may sound crazy, but it is that helpful to me.  I grew up with gospel quartet music, and this is what i love.  Thank you Canton Junction for giving me this joy....make some more DVDs for us!

Great group of guys. Their harmony is terrific.  Can't wait to see them in concert.
Gospel music at its finist.
I would definitely recommend this video.  Canton Junction is a great group with their own sound.  We were there for the taping.  So great keepsake.
I enjoyed seeing Tim Duncan back on a stage again.  Don't overlook the bonus tracks!  They are just as fun as the rest of the DVD.
If you like southern gospel music you will lobe this.  It is so good & such a blessing! Can't go wrong with this one.
I really loved this video.  The songs were really great.  This was truly an uplifting video, I did like the humor that was in it as well.  I would buy other products from this artist.

I purchased the CD as well as DVD and you can feel their love for The Lord as they sing and perform to praise Him!!! Everyone that loves gospel...praise....comtemporary or the older songs that many of us know by heart from our early years in church; I believe you will be truly blessed by this group and their music.
Canton Junction is always remarkable in their music- Wow- what voices
